Author: Ice
Name: Explorer's Icebox
Punchline: What if, we held hands underneath the quartz mountain.
Description:
A little helper that lets you level up, or gather all the materials on Island Sanctary. Requires Navmesh & Visland.
Pop open a cold one while the tedious parts of exploration is handled by your good friend cousin robby

Author: Ice, UcanPatates
Name: Root of Riches
Description:
This Plugin is meant to help you turn in your Deltascape , Gordian and Alexandrian parts. (O1-4N, A9-12, and A1-4). 

This also has a built in farming mode for A4N, so you can grind to your hearts content.
Changelog:
Fixed buying from a 2nd/3rd shop (hopefully fixing omega and alexander shop)  
Added checkmarks for necessary things for Normal Mode Raid Farms
